 |work=Boston.com Reiss\u2019 Pieces |first=Mike |last=Reiss |date=November 6, 2007 |accessdate=November 7, 2007 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121022154054/http://www.boston.com/sports/football/patriots/reiss_pieces/2007/11/patssteelers_41.html |archivedate=October 22, 2012 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>}}|| December 9, 2007 || [[2007 Pittsburgh Steelers season|Pittsburgh Steelers]] || '''W''' 34\u201313 || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 13\u20130 || Gillette Stadium || CBS || [https://web.archive.org/web/20080108020222/http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/recap?game_id=29394&displayPage=tab_recap&season=2007&week=REG14 Recap]\n|- style=\"background:#dfd;\"\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 15 ||1:00&nbsp;PM EST|| December 16, 2007 || '''[[2007 New York Jets season|New York Jets]]''' || '''W''' 20\u201310 || style=\"text-align:center;\"| 14\u20130 || Gillette Stadium || CBS || [https://web.archive.org/web/20080106102918/http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/recap?game_id=29409&displayPage=tab_recap&season=2007&week=REG15&override=true Recap]\n|- style=\"background:#dfd;\"\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 16 ||4:15&nbsp;PM EST{{efn|Game moved from 1:00&nbsp;PM to 4:15 on CBS under NFL \u201cflex scheduling\u201d rules<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.boston.com/sports/football/patriots/reiss_pieces/2007/12/ |title=Pats-Dolphins to 4:15 |work=Boston.com Reiss\u2019 Pieces |first=Mike |last=Reiss |date=December 10, 2007 |accessdate=December 10, 2007 |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081225154403/http://www.boston.com/sports/football/patriots/reiss_pieces/2007/12/ |archivedate=December 25, 2008 |df=mdy-all }}</ref>}}|| December 23, 2007 || '''[[2007 Miami Dolphins season|Miami Dolphins]]''' || '''W''' 28\u20137 ||align=center| 15\u20130 || Gillette Stadium || CBS || [https://web.archive.org/web/20080102183135/http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/recap?game_id=29428&displayPage=tab_recap&season=2007&week=REG16 Recap]\n|- style=\"background:#dfd;\"\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 17 ||8:15&nbsp;PM EST|| December 29, 2007 || at [[2007 New York Giants season|New York Giants]] || '''W''' 38\u201335 ||align=center| 16\u20130 || Giants Stadium || [[Run to the Playoffs|NFLN]]{{ref label|simulcast|b|b}} ||[https://web.archive.org/web/20080102020228/http://www.nfl.com/gamecenter/recap?game_id=29435&displayPage=tab_recap&season=2007&week=REG17 Recap]\n|}\n:{{note label|simulcast|a|a}} Simulcast on [[WCVB-TV]] and [[WMUR-TV]].\n:{{note label|simulcast|b|b}} Simulcast on CBS, NBC, [[WMUR-TV]], [[WWOR-TV]], and [[WCVB-TV]].\n\n==Week 1 roster==\n{| class=\"toccolours\" style=\"text-align: left;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"9\" style=\"background:#0d254c; color:#d6d6d6; text-align:center;\"|'''New England Patriots 2007 Week 1 roster'''\n|-\n|  style=\"font-size:95%; vertical-align:top;\"| '''Quarterbacks'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">12</span> [[Tom Brady]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">16</span> [[Matt Cassel]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">&nbsp;7</span> [[Matt Gutierrez]] <sup>UR</sup>\n\n'''Running Backs'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">44</span> [[Heath Evans]] FB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">33</span> [[Kevin Faulk]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">39</span> [[Laurence Maroney]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">34</span> [[Sammy Morris]]\n\n'''Wide Receivers'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">10</span> [[Jabar Gaffney]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">81</span> [[Randy Moss]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">18</span> [[Dont\u00e9 Stallworth]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">15</span> [[Kelley Washington]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">83</span> [[Wes Welker]] PR\n\n'''Tight Ends'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">88</span> [[Kyle Brady]]\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">86</span> [[David Thomas (American football)|David Thomas]]\n* <span