otball)|Billy Yates]] G/C\n\n'''Defensive Linemen'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">97</span> [[Jarvis Green]] DE\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">95</span> [[Rashad Moore]] NT\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">93</span> [[Richard Seymour]] DE\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">90</span> [[Le Kevin Smith]] DE/NT\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">92</span> [[Santonio Thomas]] DE/NT\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">94</span> [[Ty Warren]] DE\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">75</span> [[Vince Wilfork]] NT\n| style=\"width: 25px;\" |\n|  style=\"font-size:95%; vertical-align:top;\"| '''Linebackers'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">52</span> [[Eric Alexander (American football)|Eric Alexander]] ILB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">54</span> [[Tedy Bruschi]] ILB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">53</span> [[Larry Izzo]] ILB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">55</span> [[Junior Seau]] ILB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">96</span> [[Adalius Thomas]] OLB/DE\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">50</span> [[Mike Vrabel]] OLB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">58</span> [[Pierre Woods]] OLB\n\n'''Defensive Backs'''\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">23</span> [[Willie Andrews]] SS\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">21</span> [[Randall Gay]] CB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">37</span> [[Rodney Harrison]] SS\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">27</span> [[Ellis Hobbs]] CB/KR\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">31</span> [[Brandon Meriweather]] FS <sup>R</sup>\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">22</span> [[Asante Samuel]] CB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">36</span> [[James Sanders (American football)|James Sanders]] FS\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">28</span> [[Antwain Spann]] CB\n* <span style=\"font-family: Courier New;\">41</span> [